{{Infobox person | name = Gay Blackstone | residence = | image = | image_size = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = March 27 | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | death_cause = | known = | occupation = Magician, Producer, Director, Creator, Consultant | title = | salary = | term = | predecessor = | successor = | party = | boards = Arts and Letters - CSUSB, Ronald McDonald House | religion = | spouse = [[Harry Blackstone Jr.]] (died May 14, 1997) Married 23 years. | partner = | children = Bellamie, Tracey, Adrienne, Cynthia and the late Harry Blackstone III | relations = | website = [http://www.blackstonemagic.com www.blackstonemagic.com] | footnotes = | employer = | height = | weight = }} '''Gay (also Gaye) Blackstone''' (born March 27) is an American television and stage producer, director, consultant, lecturer and author. She was president of the [[Academy of Magical Arts]]<ref name="Reporter"/> and was named one of "2007 Hollywood's Women of Distinction" by the Hollywood Chamber of Commerce.<ref>{{cite news |title=Magic World’s Gay Blackstone to Be Recognized at Hollywood Chamber Community Foundation Event, May 15 |author=[[Academy of Magical Arts]] |url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20070507005400/en/Magic-Worlds-Gay-Blackstone-Recognized-Hollywood-Chamber |newspaper=[[Business Wire]] |date=May 7, 2007 |accessdate=August 8, 2013}}</ref> She is also the international ambassador of the [[International Brotherhood of Magicians]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.insidemagic.com/magicnews/2002/11/gay-blackstone-and-sothebys-auctioning-blackstone-effects-costumes/|title=Gay Blackstone and Sotheby’s Auctioning Blackstone Effects, Costumes|author=|first=|date=November 16, 2002|newspaper=Inside Magic|accessdate=August 8, 2013|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=}}</ref> Blackstone was the executive producer for the 2013 revival of the television show ''[[Masters of Illusion (TV series)|Masters of Illusion]]''.<ref name="Reporter">{{cite news |title=CW Revives Magic Show 'Masters of Illusion' |author=Lesley Goldberg |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/cw-revives-magic-show-masters-585645 |newspaper=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=July 16, 2013 |accessdate=August 8, 2013}}</ref>
