{{DISPLAYTITLE:''Looney Tunes'' and ''Merrie Melodies'' filmography}}
This is a listing of the shorts, feature films, television programs, and television specials in [[Warner Bros.]]' ''[[Looney Tunes]]'' and ''[[Merrie Melodies]]'' series, extending from 1929 through the present. Altogether, 1,002 animated theatrical shorts alone were released under the Looney Tunes and Merrie Melodies banners from the 1930s through the 1960s (1000 official and 2 cut downs). From the beginning to the present day, 1,041 shorts have been created.

