{{Use British English|date=April 2016}}
{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2016}}
'''WhatsOnStage.com''' is a London-based website that provides information about, and offers tickets for, theatrical performances in the United Kingdom. It also organises the annual [[WhatsOnStage Awards]]. Founded in 1996, it has been owned by the American company TheaterMania.com since January 2013.<ref name="About">{{cite web | url=https://www.whatsonstage.com/info/about | title=About Us | publisher=www.whatsonstage.com | accessdate=29 September 2018}}</ref> Its chief operating officer is Sita McIntosh.<ref name="Hutchison">{{cite news | url=https://www.thestage.co.uk/news/2016/michael-coveney-steps-down-from-whatsonstage-after-10-years/ | work = [[The Stage]]|title=Michael Coveney steps down from WhatsOnStage after 10 years | date=11 March 2016 | accessdate=5 April 2016 | author=Hutchison, David}}</ref>

